% ----------------------
\section{Discussion}
% ----------------------

\begin{frame}{Discussion}
\begin{itemize}
  \item FCOVER provides insight into long-term vegetation dynamics.
  \item Cropping to Quito reduced cloud contamination and increased interpretability.
  \item Sentinel-2 composites differentiate vegetation and built-up land.
  \item NDVI confirms changes in vegetation health between 2016 and 2024.
\end{itemize}
\end{frame}

